OL,3,CQueen of one of Longleat's prides of
OL,4,Clions dies just before her 21st
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FKeepers at the Longleat Estate in
OL,8,FWiltshire have announced that one the
OL,9,FQueen of one of their prides has died
OL,10,Fjust months before her 21st birthday.
OL,12,FIn the wild lions tend to live for
OL,13,Fbetween 12 and 14 years.
OL,15,FJasira was the matriarch in Klaus and
OL,16,FSimba's pride on the Wiltshire estate
OL,17,Fand passed away after a short illness.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
