CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783675170
OL,3,CQueen of one of Longleat's prides of
OL,4,Clions dies just before her 21st
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FShe was one of the oldest lions in
OL,8,Fhuman care in the UK following the
OL,9,Fdeath of her half-sister Malaika last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FCarnivore Team Manager Amy Waller
OL,13,Fsaid: "Several of our lions have or
OL,14,Fare reaching this grand age, and
OL,15,Fwhilst it always sad when we lose an
OL,16,Fanimal, particularly a stalwart like
OL,17,FJasira, we are very proud that she
OL,18,Flived as long as she did as her age is
OL,19,Ftestament to the care she received
OL,20,Fhere."
OL,26,@uD@GOU|D@FO]
