OL,3,CQueen of one of Longleat's prides of
OL,4,Clions dies just before her 21st
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FLongleat introduced the first Drive-
OL,8,FThrough Safari Park outside of Africa
OL,9,F60 years ago and recently started
OL,10,Fcreating a new pride with the arrival
OL,11,Fof two female southern lions.
OL,13,FThe naming of the new arrivals has
OL,14,Fbeen open to public vote with the
OL,15,Fwinners due to be announced later this
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
